{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"I'm very fortunate to be here."},{"time":2000,"text":"I feel so fortunate."},{"time":4000,"text":"I've been so impressed by the kindness expressed to me."},{"time":8000,"text":"I called my wife Leslie,"},{"time":10000,"text":"and I said, \"You know, there's so many good people"},{"time":12000,"text":"trying to do so much good."},{"time":14000,"text":"It feels like I've landed in a colony of angels.\""},{"time":18000,"text":"It's a true feeling."},{"time":21000,"text":"But let me get to the talk -- I see the clock is running."}]},{"cues":[{"time":24000,"text":"I'm a public school teacher,"},{"time":27000,"text":"and I just want to share a story of my superintendent."},{"time":30000,"text":"Her name is Pam Moran"},{"time":32000,"text":"in Albemarle County, Virginia,"},{"time":34000,"text":"the foothills of the Blue Ridge Mountains."},{"time":36000,"text":"And she's a very high-tech superintendent."},{"time":38000,"text":"She uses smart boards, she blogs,"},{"time":40000,"text":"she Tweets, she does Facebook,"},{"time":42000,"text":"she does all this sort of high-tech stuff."},{"time":44000,"text":"She's a technology leader and instructional leader."},{"time":47000,"text":"But in her office,"},{"time":49000,"text":"there's this old wooden, weather-worn table, kitchen table --"},{"time":53000,"text":"peeling green paint, it's kind of rickety."},{"time":56000,"text":"And I said, \"Pam, you're such a modern, cutting-edge person."},{"time":60000,"text":"Why is this old table in your office?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":62000,"text":"And she told me, she said,"},{"time":64000,"text":"\"You know, I grew up in Southwestern Virginia,"},{"time":67000,"text":"in the coal mines and the farmlands of rural Virginia,"},{"time":70000,"text":"and this table was in my grandfather's kitchen."},{"time":74000,"text":"And we'd come in from playing, he'd come in from plowing and working,"},{"time":77000,"text":"and we'd sit around that table every night."},{"time":79000,"text":"And as I grew up, I heard so much knowledge"},{"time":82000,"text":"and so many insights and so much wisdom"},{"time":84000,"text":"come out around this table,"},{"time":86000,"text":"I began to call it the wisdom table."},{"time":89000,"text":"And when he passed on, I took this table with me and brought it to my office,"},{"time":92000,"text":"and it reminds me of him."},{"time":94000,"text":"It reminds me of what goes on around an empty space sometimes.\""},{"time":99000,"text":"The project I'm going to tell you about"},{"time":101000,"text":"is called the World Peace Game,"},{"time":103000,"text":"and essentially it is also an empty space."},{"time":105000,"text":"And I'd like to think of it"},{"time":107000,"text":"as a 21st century wisdom table, really."}]},{"cues":[{"time":111000,"text":"It all started back in 1977."},{"time":115000,"text":"I was a young man,"},{"time":118000,"text":"and I had been dropping in and out of college."},{"time":125000,"text":"And my parents were very patient,"},{"time":128000,"text":"but I had been doing intermittent sojourns to India"},{"time":130000,"text":"on a mystical quest."},{"time":132000,"text":"And I remember the last time I came back from India --"},{"time":134000,"text":"in my long white flowing robes"},{"time":136000,"text":"and my big beard and my John Lennon glasses --"},{"time":139000,"text":"and I said to my father,"},{"time":141000,"text":"\"Dad, I think I've just about found spiritual enlightenment.\""},{"time":143000,"text":"He said, \"Well there's one more thing you need to find.\""},{"time":146000,"text":"I said, \"What is that, dad?\" \"A job.\""},{"time":149000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":152000,"text":"And so they pleaded with me to get a degree in something."},{"time":155000,"text":"So I got a degree"},{"time":157000,"text":"and it turned out to be education."},{"time":159000,"text":"It was an experimental education program."},{"time":161000,"text":"It could have been dentistry, but the word \"experimental\" was in it,"},{"time":163000,"text":"and so that's what I had to go for."}]},{"cues":[{"time":166000,"text":"And I went in for a job interview"},{"time":169000,"text":"in the Richmond Public Schools in Virginia, the capital city,"},{"time":172000,"text":"bought a three-piece suit -- my concession to convention --"},{"time":175000,"text":"kept my long beard and my afro"},{"time":177000,"text":"and my platform shoes -- at the time it was the '70s --"},{"time":180000,"text":"and I walked in, and I sat down and had an interview."},{"time":183000,"text":"And I guess they were hard up for teachers"},{"time":185000,"text":"because the supervisor, her name was Anna Aro,"},{"time":187000,"text":"said I had the job teaching gifted children."},{"time":191000,"text":"And I was so shocked, so stunned,"},{"time":193000,"text":"I got up and said, \"Well, thank you, but what do I do?\""},{"time":196000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":199000,"text":"Gifted education hadn't really taken hold too much."},{"time":201000,"text":"There weren't really many materials or things to use."},{"time":204000,"text":"And I said, \"What do I do?\""},{"time":206000,"text":"And her answer shocked me. It stunned me."},{"time":209000,"text":"Her answer set the template"},{"time":211000,"text":"for the entire career I was to have after that."},{"time":215000,"text":"She said, \"What do you want to do?\""},{"time":220000,"text":"And that question cleared the space."},{"time":222000,"text":"There was no program directive, no manual to follow,"},{"time":225000,"text":"no standards in gifted education"},{"time":228000,"text":"in that way."},{"time":230000,"text":"And she cleared such a space"},{"time":232000,"text":"that I endeavored from then on"},{"time":234000,"text":"to clear a space for my students, an empty space,"},{"time":237000,"text":"whereby they could create and make meaning"},{"time":239000,"text":"out of their own understanding."}]},{"cues":[{"time":243000,"text":"So this happened in 1978,"},{"time":246000,"text":"and I was teaching many years later,"},{"time":249000,"text":"and a friend of mine introduced me to a young filmmaker."},{"time":252000,"text":"His name is Chris Farina."},{"time":254000,"text":"Chris Farina is here today at his own cost."},{"time":256000,"text":"Chris, could you stand up and let them see you --"},{"time":258000,"text":"a young, visionary filmmaker who's made a film."},{"time":261000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":265000,"text":"This film is called \"World Peace and Other 4th Grade Achievements.\""},{"time":268000,"text":"He proposed the film to me -- it's a great title."},{"time":271000,"text":"He proposed the film to me,"},{"time":273000,"text":"and I said, \"Yeah, maybe it'll be on local TV,"},{"time":275000,"text":"and we can say hi to our friends.\""},{"time":277000,"text":"But the film has really gone places."},{"time":279000,"text":"Now it's still in debt, but Chris has managed, through his own sacrifice,"},{"time":282000,"text":"to get this film out."},{"time":284000,"text":"So we made a film"},{"time":286000,"text":"and it turns out to be more than a story about me,"},{"time":289000,"text":"more than a story about one teacher."},{"time":291000,"text":"It's a story that's a testament to teaching and teachers."},{"time":295000,"text":"And it's a beautiful thing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":297000,"text":"And the strange thing is, when I watch the film --"},{"time":300000,"text":"I have the eerie sensation of seeing it --"},{"time":303000,"text":"I saw myself literally disappear."},{"time":306000,"text":"What I saw"},{"time":308000,"text":"was my teachers coming through me."},{"time":312000,"text":"I saw my geometry teacher in high school, Mr. Rucell's"},{"time":316000,"text":"wry smile under his handlebar mustache."},{"time":319000,"text":"That's the smile I use -- that's his smile."},{"time":322000,"text":"I saw Jan Polo's flashing eyes."},{"time":325000,"text":"And they weren't flashing in anger,"},{"time":327000,"text":"they were flashing in love, intense love for her students."},{"time":330000,"text":"And I have that kind of flash sometimes."},{"time":333000,"text":"And I saw Miss Ethel J. Banks"},{"time":336000,"text":"who wore pearls and high-heels to elementary school every day."},{"time":340000,"text":"And you know, she had that old-school teacher stare."},{"time":344000,"text":"You know the one."},{"time":346000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":349000,"text":"\"And I'm not even talking about you behind me,"},{"time":351000,"text":"because I've got eyes in the back of my head.\""},{"time":353000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":356000,"text":"You know that teacher?"},{"time":358000,"text":"I didn't use that stare very often,"},{"time":360000,"text":"but I do have it in my repertoire."},{"time":363000,"text":"And Miss Banks was there as a great mentor for me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":366000,"text":"And then I saw"},{"time":368000,"text":"my own parents, my first teachers."},{"time":371000,"text":"My father, very inventive, spatial thinker."},{"time":374000,"text":"That's my brother Malcolm there on the right."},{"time":377000,"text":"And my mother,"},{"time":379000,"text":"who taught me in fourth grade"},{"time":381000,"text":"in segregated schools in Virginia,"},{"time":383000,"text":"who was my inspiration."},{"time":386000,"text":"And really, I feel as though,"},{"time":388000,"text":"when I see the film --"},{"time":390000,"text":"I have a gesture she does, like this --"},{"time":393000,"text":"I feel like I am a continuation of her gesture."},{"time":397000,"text":"I am one of her teaching gestures."},{"time":399000,"text":"And the beautiful thing was,"},{"time":401000,"text":"I got to teach my daughter in elementary school, Madeline."},{"time":404000,"text":"And so that gesture of my mother's"},{"time":406000,"text":"continues through many generations."},{"time":408000,"text":"It's an amazing feeling"},{"time":410000,"text":"to have that lineage."},{"time":412000,"text":"And so I'm here standing on the shoulders of many people."},{"time":414000,"text":"I'm not here alone."},{"time":416000,"text":"There are many people on this stage right now."}]},{"cues":[{"time":420000,"text":"And so this World Peace Game I'd like to tell you about."},{"time":424000,"text":"It started out like this:"},{"time":426000,"text":"it's just a four-foot by five-foot plywood board"},{"time":429000,"text":"in an inner-city urban school, 1978."},{"time":432000,"text":"I was creating a lesson for students on Africa."},{"time":434000,"text":"We put all the problems of the world there,"},{"time":436000,"text":"and I thought, let's let them solve it."},{"time":438000,"text":"I didn't want to lecture or have just book reading."},{"time":441000,"text":"I wanted to have them be immersed"},{"time":443000,"text":"and learn the feeling of learning through their bodies."},{"time":447000,"text":"So I thought, well they like to play games."},{"time":449000,"text":"I'll make something -- I didn't say interactive;"},{"time":451000,"text":"we didn't have that term in 1978 --"},{"time":453000,"text":"but something interactive."},{"time":455000,"text":"And so we made the game,"},{"time":457000,"text":"and it has since evolved"},{"time":459000,"text":"to a four-foot by four-foot by four-foot"},{"time":462000,"text":"Plexiglass structure."},{"time":465000,"text":"And it has four Plexiglass layers."}]},{"cues":[{"time":468000,"text":"There's an outer space layer"},{"time":470000,"text":"with black holes and satellites"},{"time":472000,"text":"and research satellites and asteroid mining."},{"time":474000,"text":"There's an air and space level"},{"time":476000,"text":"with clouds that are big puffs of cotton we push around"},{"time":478000,"text":"and territorial air spaces and air forces,"},{"time":480000,"text":"a ground and sea level with thousands of game pieces on it --"},{"time":483000,"text":"even an undersea level"},{"time":485000,"text":"with submarines and undersea mining."},{"time":487000,"text":"There are four countries around the board."},{"time":489000,"text":"The kids make up the names of the countries -- some are rich; some are poor."},{"time":492000,"text":"They have different assets, commercial and military."},{"time":495000,"text":"And each country has a cabinet."},{"time":497000,"text":"There's a Prime Minister, Secretary of State, Minister of Defense"},{"time":499000,"text":"and a CFO, or Comptroller."},{"time":502000,"text":"I choose the Prime Minister based on my relationship with them."},{"time":505000,"text":"I offer them the job, they can turn it down,"},{"time":507000,"text":"and then they choose their own cabinet."},{"time":509000,"text":"There's a World Bank, arms dealers and a United Nations."},{"time":512000,"text":"There's also a weather goddess"},{"time":514000,"text":"who controls a random stock market and random weather."}]},{"cues":[{"time":517000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":519000,"text":"That's not all."},{"time":521000,"text":"And then there's a 13-page crisis document"},{"time":523000,"text":"with 50 interlocking problems."},{"time":525000,"text":"So that, if one thing changes, everything else changes."},{"time":528000,"text":"I throw them into this complex matrix,"},{"time":531000,"text":"and they trust me because we have a deep, rich relationship together."},{"time":536000,"text":"And so with all these crises,"},{"time":538000,"text":"we have -- let's see -- ethnic and minority tensions;"},{"time":541000,"text":"we have chemical and nuclear spills,"},{"time":543000,"text":"nuclear proliferation."},{"time":545000,"text":"There's oil spills, environmental disasters,"},{"time":548000,"text":"water rights disputes, breakaway republics,"},{"time":551000,"text":"famine, endangered species and global warming."},{"time":553000,"text":"If Al Gore is here,"},{"time":555000,"text":"I'm going to send my fourth-graders from Agnor-Hurt and Venable schools to you"},{"time":558000,"text":"because they solved global warming in a week."},{"time":561000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":563000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":566000,"text":"And they've done it several times too."}]},{"cues":[{"time":569000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":571000,"text":"So I also have in the game a saboteur --"},{"time":574000,"text":"some child -- it's basically a troublemaker --"},{"time":577000,"text":"and I have my troublemaker put to use"},{"time":580000,"text":"because they, on the surface,"},{"time":582000,"text":"are trying to save the world and their position in the game."},{"time":584000,"text":"But they're also trying to undermine everything in the game."},{"time":588000,"text":"And they do it secretly through misinformation"},{"time":590000,"text":"and ambiguities and irrelevancies,"},{"time":592000,"text":"trying to cause everyone to think more deeply."},{"time":594000,"text":"The saboteur is there,"},{"time":596000,"text":"and we also read from Sun Tzu's \"The Art of War.\""},{"time":598000,"text":"Fourth-graders understand it -- nine years old --"},{"time":601000,"text":"and they handle that and use that"},{"time":603000,"text":"to understand how to, not follow --"},{"time":605000,"text":"at first they do --"},{"time":607000,"text":"the paths to power and destruction,"},{"time":609000,"text":"the path to war."},{"time":611000,"text":"They learn to overlook short-sighted reactions"},{"time":613000,"text":"and impulsive thinking,"},{"time":615000,"text":"to think in a long-term, more consequential way."}]},{"cues":[{"time":619000,"text":"Stewart Brand is here, and one of the ideas for this game came from him"},{"time":622000,"text":"with a CoEvolution Quarterly article"},{"time":624000,"text":"on a peace force."},{"time":626000,"text":"And in the game, sometimes students actually form a peace force."},{"time":629000,"text":"I'm just a clock watcher."},{"time":632000,"text":"I'm just a clarifier. I'm just a facilitator."},{"time":634000,"text":"The students run the game."},{"time":636000,"text":"I have no chance to make any policy whatsoever"},{"time":638000,"text":"once they start playing."},{"time":640000,"text":"So I'll just share with you ..."}]},{"cues":[{"time":643000,"text":"(Video) Boy: The World Peace Game is serious."},{"time":645000,"text":"You're actually getting taught something like how to take care of the world."},{"time":648000,"text":"See, Mr. Hunter is doing that"},{"time":650000,"text":"because he says his time has messed up a lot,"},{"time":652000,"text":"and he's trying to tell us"},{"time":654000,"text":"how to fix that problem."}]},{"cues":[{"time":656000,"text":"John Hunter: I offered them a --"},{"time":658000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":661000,"text":"Actually, I can't tell them anything because I don't know the answer."},{"time":664000,"text":"And I admit the truth to them right up front: I don't know."},{"time":667000,"text":"And because I don't know, they've got to dig up the answer."},{"time":670000,"text":"And so I apologize to them as well."},{"time":672000,"text":"I say, \"I'm so sorry, boys and girls,"},{"time":675000,"text":"but the truth is"},{"time":677000,"text":"we have left this world to you in such a sad and terrible shape,"},{"time":680000,"text":"and we hope you can fix it for us,"},{"time":682000,"text":"and maybe this game will help you learn how to do it.\""},{"time":684000,"text":"It's a sincere apology,"},{"time":686000,"text":"and they take it very seriously."}]},{"cues":[{"time":688000,"text":"Now you may be wondering what all this complexity looks like."},{"time":691000,"text":"Well when we have the game start, here's what you see."}]},{"cues":[{"time":694000,"text":"(Video) JH: All right, we're going into negotiations as of now. Go."},{"time":697000,"text":"(Chatter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":705000,"text":"JH: My question to you is, who's in charge of that classroom?"},{"time":709000,"text":"It's a serious question: who is really in charge?"},{"time":712000,"text":"I've learned to cede control of the classroom"},{"time":714000,"text":"over to the students over time."},{"time":716000,"text":"There's a trust and an understanding"},{"time":718000,"text":"and a dedication to an ideal"},{"time":720000,"text":"that I simply don't have to do"},{"time":722000,"text":"what I thought I had to do as a beginning teacher:"},{"time":724000,"text":"control every conversation and response in the classroom."},{"time":727000,"text":"It's impossible. Their collective wisdom"},{"time":729000,"text":"is much greater than mine,"},{"time":731000,"text":"and I admit it to them openly."},{"time":734000,"text":"So I'll just share with you some stories very quickly"},{"time":737000,"text":"of some magical things that have happened."}]},{"cues":[{"time":740000,"text":"In this game we had a little girl,"},{"time":743000,"text":"and she was the Defense Minister of the poorest nation."},{"time":746000,"text":"And the Defense Minister -- she had the tank corps and Air Force and so forth."},{"time":750000,"text":"And she was next door to a very wealthy, oil-rich neighbor."},{"time":753000,"text":"Without provocation,"},{"time":755000,"text":"suddenly she attacked, against her Prime Minister's orders,"},{"time":758000,"text":"the next-door neighbor's oil fields."},{"time":760000,"text":"She marched into the oil field reserves,"},{"time":762000,"text":"surrounded it, without firing a shot,"},{"time":764000,"text":"and secured it and held it."},{"time":766000,"text":"And that neighbor was unable to conduct any military operations"},{"time":768000,"text":"because their fuel supply was locked up."}]},{"cues":[{"time":771000,"text":"We were all upset with her, \"Why are you doing this?"},{"time":773000,"text":"This is the World Peace Game. What is wrong with you?\""},{"time":775000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":777000,"text":"This was a little girl and, at nine years old,"},{"time":779000,"text":"she held her pieces and said, \"I know what I'm doing.\""},{"time":782000,"text":"To her girlfriends she said that."},{"time":785000,"text":"That's a breach there."},{"time":787000,"text":"And we learned in this, you don't really ever want to cross"},{"time":789000,"text":"a nine year-old girl with tanks."},{"time":791000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":793000,"text":"They are the toughest opponents."},{"time":796000,"text":"And we were very upset."},{"time":798000,"text":"I thought I was failing as a teacher. Why would she do this?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":801000,"text":"But come to find out, a few game days later --"},{"time":803000,"text":"and there are turns where we take negotiation from a team --"},{"time":807000,"text":"actually there's a negotiation period with all teams,"},{"time":810000,"text":"and each team takes a turn,"},{"time":812000,"text":"then we go back in negotiation, around and around,"},{"time":814000,"text":"so each turn around is one game day."},{"time":816000,"text":"So a few game days later it came to light"},{"time":819000,"text":"that we found out this major country"},{"time":821000,"text":"was planning a military offensive"},{"time":823000,"text":"to dominate the entire world."},{"time":826000,"text":"Had they had their fuel supplies, they would have done it."},{"time":828000,"text":"She was able to see the vectors and trend lines and intentions"},{"time":831000,"text":"long before any of us"},{"time":833000,"text":"and understand what was going to happen"},{"time":835000,"text":"and made a philosophical decision"},{"time":837000,"text":"to attack in a peace game."}]},{"cues":[{"time":840000,"text":"Now she used a small war to avert a larger war,"},{"time":843000,"text":"so we stopped and had a very good philosophical discussion"},{"time":845000,"text":"about whether that was right,"},{"time":847000,"text":"conditional good, or not right."},{"time":850000,"text":"That's the kind of thinking that we put them in, the situations."},{"time":853000,"text":"I could not have designed that in teaching it."},{"time":855000,"text":"It came about spontaneously through their collective wisdom."}]},{"cues":[{"time":858000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":864000,"text":"Another example, a beautiful thing happened."},{"time":866000,"text":"We have a letter in the game."},{"time":868000,"text":"If you're a military commander and you wage troops --"},{"time":870000,"text":"the little plastic toys on the board -- and you lose them,"},{"time":873000,"text":"I put in a letter."},{"time":875000,"text":"You have to write a letter to their parents --"},{"time":878000,"text":"the fictional parents of your fictional troops --"},{"time":880000,"text":"explaining what happened and offering your condolences."},{"time":883000,"text":"So you have a little bit more thought"},{"time":885000,"text":"before you commit to combat."},{"time":888000,"text":"And so we had this situation come up --"},{"time":890000,"text":"last summer actually,"},{"time":892000,"text":"at Agnor-Hurt School in Albemarle County --"},{"time":895000,"text":"and one of our military commanders got up to read that letter"},{"time":898000,"text":"and one of the other kids said, \"Mr. Hunter,"},{"time":900000,"text":"let's ask -- there's a parent over there.\""},{"time":902000,"text":"There was a parent visiting that day, just sitting in the back of the room."},{"time":904000,"text":"\"Let's ask that mom to read the letter."},{"time":906000,"text":"It'll be more realer if she reads it.\""},{"time":908000,"text":"So we did, we asked her, and she gamely picked up the letter."},{"time":911000,"text":"\"Sure.\" She started reading. She read one sentence."},{"time":914000,"text":"She read two sentences."},{"time":917000,"text":"By the third sentence, she was in tears."},{"time":920000,"text":"I was in tears."},{"time":923000,"text":"Everybody understood"},{"time":925000,"text":"that when we lose somebody, the winners are not gloating."},{"time":928000,"text":"We all lose."},{"time":931000,"text":"And it was an amazing occurrence and an amazing understanding."}]},{"cues":[{"time":933000,"text":"I'll show you what my friend David says about this."},{"time":935000,"text":"He's been in many battles."}]},{"cues":[{"time":937000,"text":"(Video) David: We've really had enough of people attacking."},{"time":939000,"text":"I mean, we've been lucky [most of] the time."},{"time":943000,"text":"But now I'm feeling really weird"},{"time":945000,"text":"because I'm living what Sun Tzu said one week."},{"time":949000,"text":"One week he said,"},{"time":951000,"text":"\"Those who go into battle and win"},{"time":953000,"text":"will want to go back,"},{"time":955000,"text":"and those who lose in battle"},{"time":957000,"text":"will want to go back and win.\""},{"time":960000,"text":"And so I've been winning battles,"},{"time":962000,"text":"so I'm going into battles, more battles."},{"time":965000,"text":"And I think it's sort of weird to be living"},{"time":967000,"text":"what Sun Tzu said."}]},{"cues":[{"time":971000,"text":"JH: I get chills every time I see that."},{"time":974000,"text":"That's the kind of engagement you want to have happen."},{"time":977000,"text":"And I can't design that, I can't plan that,"},{"time":980000,"text":"and I can't even test that."},{"time":982000,"text":"But it's self-evident assessment."},{"time":984000,"text":"We know that's an authentic assessment of learning."},{"time":989000,"text":"We have a lot of data, but I think sometimes we go beyond data"},{"time":992000,"text":"with the real truth of what's going on."}]},{"cues":[{"time":995000,"text":"So I'll just share a third story."},{"time":998000,"text":"This is about my friend Brennan."},{"time":1001000,"text":"We had played the game one session after school"},{"time":1004000,"text":"for many weeks, about seven weeks,"},{"time":1007000,"text":"and we had essentially solved all 50 of the interlocking crises."},{"time":1010000,"text":"The way the game is won is all 50 problems have to be solved"},{"time":1013000,"text":"and every country's asset value"},{"time":1015000,"text":"has to be increased above its starting point."},{"time":1017000,"text":"Some are poor, some are wealthy. There are billions."},{"time":1020000,"text":"The World Bank president was a third-grader one time."},{"time":1022000,"text":"He says, \"How many zeros in a trillion? I've got to calculate that right away.\""},{"time":1025000,"text":"But he was setting fiscal policy in that game"},{"time":1027000,"text":"for high school players who were playing with him."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1030000,"text":"So the team that was the poorest"},{"time":1033000,"text":"had gotten even poorer."},{"time":1035000,"text":"There was no way they could win."},{"time":1037000,"text":"And we were approaching four o'clock, our cut-off time --"},{"time":1039000,"text":"there was about a minute left --"},{"time":1041000,"text":"and despair just settled over the room."},{"time":1043000,"text":"I thought, I'm failing as a teacher."},{"time":1045000,"text":"I should have gotten it so they could have won."},{"time":1048000,"text":"They shouldn't be failing like this."},{"time":1051000,"text":"I've failed them."},{"time":1054000,"text":"And I was just feeling so sad and dejected."},{"time":1056000,"text":"And suddenly, Brennan walked over to my chair"},{"time":1058000,"text":"and he grabbed the bell, the bell I ring"},{"time":1060000,"text":"to signal a change or a reconvening of cabinets,"},{"time":1062000,"text":"and he ran back to his seat, rang the bell."},{"time":1064000,"text":"Everybody ran to his chair: there was screaming;"},{"time":1066000,"text":"there was yelling, waving of their dossiers."},{"time":1068000,"text":"They get these dossiers full of secret documents."},{"time":1070000,"text":"They were gesticulating; they were running around."},{"time":1072000,"text":"I didn't know what they were doing. I'd lost control of my classroom."},{"time":1076000,"text":"Principal walks in, I'm out of a job."},{"time":1079000,"text":"The parents were looking in the window."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1081000,"text":"And Brennan runs back to his seat. Everybody runs back to their seat."},{"time":1084000,"text":"He rings the bell again. He says, \"We have\" --"},{"time":1086000,"text":"and there's 12 seconds left on the clock --"},{"time":1088000,"text":"\"we have, all nations, pooled all our funds together."},{"time":1091000,"text":"And we've got 600 billion dollars."},{"time":1093000,"text":"We're going to offer it as a donation to this poor country."},{"time":1095000,"text":"And if they accept it, it'll raise their asset value and we can win the game."},{"time":1098000,"text":"Will you accept it?\""},{"time":1100000,"text":"And there are three seconds left on the clock."},{"time":1102000,"text":"Everybody looks at this prime minister of that country,"},{"time":1105000,"text":"and he says, \"Yes.\""},{"time":1107000,"text":"And the game is won."},{"time":1110000,"text":"Spontaneous compassion"},{"time":1113000,"text":"that could not be planned for,"},{"time":1115000,"text":"that was unexpected and unpredictable."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1118000,"text":"Every game we play is different."},{"time":1120000,"text":"Some games are more about social issues,"},{"time":1122000,"text":"some are more about economic issues."},{"time":1124000,"text":"Some games are more about warfare."},{"time":1126000,"text":"But I don't try to deny them that reality of being human."},{"time":1129000,"text":"I allow them to go there"},{"time":1131000,"text":"and, through their own experience, learn, in a bloodless way,"},{"time":1135000,"text":"how not to do what they consider to be the wrong thing."},{"time":1138000,"text":"And they find out what is right"},{"time":1140000,"text":"their own way, their own selves."},{"time":1143000,"text":"And so in this game,"},{"time":1145000,"text":"I've learned so much from it,"},{"time":1147000,"text":"but I would say"},{"time":1149000,"text":"that if only"},{"time":1152000,"text":"they could pick up a critical thinking tool"},{"time":1154000,"text":"or creative thinking tool"},{"time":1156000,"text":"from this game"},{"time":1158000,"text":"and leverage something good for the world,"},{"time":1162000,"text":"they may save us all."},{"time":1165000,"text":"If only."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1168000,"text":"And on behalf of all of my teachers"},{"time":1170000,"text":"on whose shoulders I'm standing,"},{"time":1172000,"text":"thank you. Thank you. Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1175000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}